FileHippoUpdateDownloader

Utility that downloads updates found by the FileHippo Update Checker.

To use, open the Update Checker's settings, and set the Custom Browser
option to 'DRIVE:\path\to\FileHippoUpdateDownloader.exe %1'.

The updates found are downloaded into a directory called
DownloadedUpdates in the folder where FileHippoUpdateDownloader.exe
resides.


The Update Checker can be found at http://filehippo.com/updatechecker/
